Tests
-----
* Test the code with databases that have spaces in the names
* Test the code on various operating systems including BSD; try to make it as portable as possible

Funcionality
-------------
* Support to direct output to log file
  - Log file should be configurable

Package Management
------------------
* Packages for popular operating systems, Ubuntu, CentOS, FreeBSD
  - Installer should automatically register a crontab in the daily crontab for root

Utilities
---------
* Separate scripts to retrieve backups and optionally load them into the database
